<h1>Financial Decisions for Life After College</h1>

<h4>[formerly, Making Cent$ of Money - first started 2007-03-26]</h4>
<h4>Organized and presented by Professors Al Hibbard and Mark Mills</h4>

<!-- 
<p>
[Also found here (but perhaps an older version): <a href="https://my.central.edu/Student-Services/Career-Services/Pages/Financial-Decisions-for-Life-After-College.aspx" target="_blank">https://my.central.edu/Student-Services/Career-Services/Pages/Financial-Decisions-for-Life-After-College.aspx</a>]
</p>
