			<li>Health insurance and health spending (<a href="https://www.cms.gov/cciio/resources/files/downloads/dwnlds/uniform-glossary-final.pdf" target="_blank">learn the vocabulary</a> or <a href="https://www.medmutual.com/For-Individuals-and-Families/Health-Insurance-Education/Glossary-of-Terms.aspx" target="_blank">here</a>)
